import React from "react";
import Layout from '../components/Layout';
import {Button, Card, Icon, Image} from "semantic-ui-react";

const UserCard = () => {
  return(
    <Layout>
      <React.Fragment style={{ margin: 0  }}>
        <Card color = "red">

          <Card.Content>
            <Card.Header>
              Anakin Skywalker
            </Card.Header>

            <Card.Meta>
              Bio
            </Card.Meta>

            <Card.Description>
              Has a dark side...
            </Card.Description>
          </Card.Content>

          <Card.Content extra>
            <Icon name = "instagram" />
            @theChosenOne
          </Card.Content>
        </Card>

        <Button primary>Add Friend</Button>

        <Button color='instagram'>
          <Icon name='instagram' /> Go To Instagram
        </Button>

      </React.Fragment>
    </Layout>
  )
}


export default UserCard
